episodes.title: Cults & Hot Yoga | Ep. 25
episodes.description:
This week the girls talk about Blake Lively's problematic Loreal campaign, friendship breakups, imposter syndrome, and Alana's near death experience in a yoga class (she's fine, but it's giving NPC). Keida also throws some insane shade at Alana (classic). The gang discusses cults they'd be most likely to lead, and which they'd be most likely to join and Jesse shares a recent realization that sparks a deeper discussion.
